flowchart TD
    A([Start: Public Website]) --> B{User Type}
    B -->|Guest| C[Register]
    C --> D[OTP Verification]
    D --> E[Login]
    B -->|Existing User| E

    E --> F{Role}
    F -->|Applicant| G[Open Applicant Dashboard]
    F -->|Admin/Staff| H[Open Admin/Staff Dashboard]

    G --> I{Application Period Open?}
    I -->|No| J[Wait / Check Announcements]
    J --> I
    I -->|Yes| K[Submit Application + Documents + Photo]
    K --> L[Application Under Review]
    L --> M[Receive Notification / SMS]
    M --> N[Track Status]

    H --> O[Review Application]
    O --> P[Verify Documents]
    P --> Q[Update Status]
    Q --> R{For Payout?}
    R -->|No| S[Send Update to Applicant]
    R -->|Yes| T[Create Disbursement]
    T --> S
    S --> N

    N --> U{Final Decision}
    U -->|Approved| V([End: Disbursed])
    U -->|Not Approved| W([End: Rejected])
